# Reference fixture waivers: the gray bus and the 4-phase handshake are safe
# by construction (one bit changes per gray step; the handshake holds the
# payload until ack returns) but not structurally provable.
waive CDC-004 .*u_gray_sync.*   gray-coded bus: one bit changes per step
waive CDC-012 .*u_hs.*          4-phase req/ack: payload held until ack returns
